    <title>数组名与数组地址</title>
    <url>/2020/05/16/%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="数组名与数组地址的简单记录">数组名与数组地址的简单记录</h1>
<blockquote>
<p>粗浅认识，请多多指教</p>
</blockquote>
<p>想写这个相关的问题，是因为在看到二维数组降维的时候，使用的是<code>&amp;iArray</code>的形式，我一想，这也是地址，为啥不用<code>iArray</code>呢。。。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/jingzi123456789/article/details/66478310" target="_blank" rel="noopener">本文引用</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="iarray与iarray是省政府和市政府的区别"><code>iArray</code>与<code>&amp;iArray</code>是省政府和市政府的区别</h2>
<p>这里有一个例子可以清晰看出差别</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> _size_ (5)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="built_in">std</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> xiArray[_size_] = &#123;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"        xArray = "</span>&lt;&lt;xiArray&lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>; <span class="comment">//-64424496976</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"       &amp;xArray = "</span>&lt;&lt; &amp;xiArray&lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"    xArray + 1 = "</span>&lt;&lt; xiArray  + <span class="number">1</span>&lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"&amp;xArray[0] + 1 = "</span>&lt;&lt;&amp;xiArray[<span class="number">0</span>] + <span class="number">1</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;<span class="comment">//-64424496972</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"   &amp;xArray + 1 = "</span>&lt;&lt; &amp;xiArray + <span class="number">1</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;<span class="comment">//-64424496956</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>得到的结果：</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        xArray = 0x1000030b0</span><br><span class="line">       &amp;xArray = 0x1000030b0</span><br><span class="line">    xArray + 1 = 0x1000030b4</span><br><span class="line">&amp;xArray[0] + 1 = 0x1000030b4</span><br><span class="line">   &amp;xArray + 1 = 0x1000030c4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>地址是16进制数，上面的注释是转化的10进制数</p>
</blockquote>
<p>这里看到，<code>&amp;xArray</code>的增量单位是数组大小<code>sizeof(_size_ * sizeof(int))</code>，而<code>xArray</code>的增量是元素类型大小<code>sizeof(int) == 4</code></p>
<p>就像省政府的增量就是下一个省政府，市政府的增量就是下一个市政府。</p>
<p>这里用指针的理论来说，<code>xArray</code>等价于<code>&amp;xArray[0]</code>，<code>&amp;xArray</code>就是本身的意思。这样就好理解了：指针的增量<code>++</code>的单位是指针类型的大小。</p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>C++</tag>
      </tags>
