    <url>/2020/06/04/%E7%94%B5%E7%A3%81%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="电磁学相似问题的独立总结">电磁学相似问题的独立总结</h1>
<blockquote>
<p>有不正确的地方会在发现之后立刻修改的。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="直接列表">直接列表</h2>
<table>
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 9%" />
<col style="width: 45%" />
<col style="width: 45%" />
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr class="header">
<th style="text-align: center;"></th>
<th style="text-align: center;">电学</th>
<th style="text-align: center;">磁学</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>场强大小</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">库伦定律(电场)：<span class="math inline">\(E = k_{1}\frac{Q}{r^{2}}\)</span></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">毕奥-萨法尔定律：<span class="math inline">\(dB=k_{2}\frac{Idl}{r^{2}}\)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>高斯定律</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">电高斯定律：通过高斯面的电场线条数和面内部的电荷量成正比</td>
<td style="text-align: center;">磁高斯定律：通过高斯面的磁感线条数为零</td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>环路定理</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(\int_{l}Eds = 0\)</span>(保守场)</td>
<td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(\int_{l}Bds = \mu I\)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>力矩相关</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">电偶极矩<span class="math inline">\(p\)</span></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">分子磁矩<span class="math inline">\(m\)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>介质极化</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">电极化强度：<span class="math inline">\(\left |\frac{\sum_{i}p_{i}}{\Delta V}\right | = \sigma\)</span>（单位体积介质表面电荷量）</td>
<td style="text-align: center;">磁化强度：<span class="math inline">\(\left |\frac{\sum m}{\Delta V}\right |=i\)</span>（单位长度介质表面分子电流）</td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>介质场强</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">介质高斯定律：<span class="math inline">\(\int Dds = q\)</span></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">介质环路定理：<span class="math inline">\(\int Hdl = I\)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>衍生关系</strong></td>
<td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(D=\sigma E\)</span></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">$B = H $</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>大概先写这么多，其他的介质间场的变化关系可以简单的推导出来，也就不赘述。</p>
]]></content>
